dct_title_s: 5-digit zip code boundaries for the United States
dct_description_sm: This dataset provides up-to-date boundary and location data for zip codes in the United States. Starting in 2004, polygon (boundary) and point (location) shapefiles are updated quarterly with feeds from the United States Postal Services and other information.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads shapefile format.
